  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.poster.avif?t=1753880211\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.webm?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.mp4?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play together:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your friend's back as either the VR player or the PC player. You can play together using the same PC, or invite someone from your Steam friends list to play using Steam Remote Play Together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Realistic Reloading:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience true-to-life weapon handling—each gun reloads and operates like its real-world counterpart. Quick reflexes and reloading precision are your keys to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.poster.avif?t=1753880211\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.webm?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.mp4?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Progression:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A robust progression system for both players which includes: Unlockable guns, attachments, player upgrades, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Loot:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and scavenge to find loot, new weapons, attachments, and more!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.poster.avif?t=1753880211\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.webm?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.mp4?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play together:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your friend's back as either the VR player or the PC player. You can play together using the same PC, or invite someone from your Steam friends list to play using Steam Remote Play Together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Realistic Reloading:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience true-to-life weapon handling—each gun reloads and operates like its real-world counterpart. Quick reflexes and reloading precision are your keys to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.poster.avif?t=1753880211\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.webm?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.mp4?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Progression:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A robust progression system for both players which includes: Unlockable guns, attachments, player upgrades, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Loot:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and scavenge to find loot, new weapons, attachments, and more!</p>",
